Description: seqfinder is a tool for processing sequences in the FASTA format.
  Including get fasta sequence base on gene id,
  get longest sequence from pep fasta or cdna fasta,
  get longest sequence id from gff file,
  get gene location information,
  get sequence information such as sequence length, mw, hydrophobicity, pI.
